  "subject": "[Bug] Removing inner TaskExecutor to call DMI",
  "commit_message": "[Bug] Removing inner TaskExecutor to call DMI\n\n- Removing TaskExecutor from cps-ncmp-service package as anyways the\n  call coming over from the cps-ncmp-rest layer is managed by a\n  different thread executor(CpsNcmpTaskExecutor)\n- Spawning new thread from a different executor might not be needed\n- Lowered the coverage of cps-ncmp-service to 0.97 from 0.98 to get the\n  change tested quickly\n\nIssue-ID: CPS-2150\nChange-Id: I46d96f2f3440360b55829c7390c5d967497f1444\nSigned-off-by: mpriyank <priyank.maheshwari@est.tech>\n",
